<div class="nass margin-top-10"> <p><span id="p1" class="anchor"></span>- وَعَكْسُهُ بِعَكْسِهِ.<a href="#p1" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p2"></span>-<span class="c5"> وَيَجِبُ:</span> إِنْ كَانَتْ عَلَى فِعْلِ مُحَرَّمٍ، أَوْ تَرْكِ وَاجِبٍ.<a href="#p2" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p3"></span>- وَعَكْسُهُ بِعَكْسِهِ.<a href="#p3" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p4"></span>فَصْلٌ<a href="#p4" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p5"></span>- وَإِنْ حَرَّمَ أَمَتَهُ،<span class="c5"> أَوْ حَلَالاً غَيْرَ زَوْجَةٍ:</span><a href="#p5" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p6"></span>- لَمْ يَحْرُمْ.<a href="#p6" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p7"></span>- وَعَلَيْهِ كَفَّارَةُ يَمِينٍ إِنْ فَعَلَهُ.<a href="#p7" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p8"></span>- وَتَجِبُ فَوْراً بِحِنْثٍ.<a href="#p8" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p9"></span>-<span class="c5"> وَيُخَيَّرُ فِيهَا بَيْنَ:</span><a href="#p9" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p10"></span>- إِطْعَامِ عَشَرَةِ مَسَاكِينَ.<a href="#p10" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p11"></span>- أَوْ كِسْوَتِهِمْ كِسْوَةً تَصِحُّ بِهَا صَلَاةُ فَرْضٍ.<a href="#p11" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p12"></span>- أَوْ عِتْقِ رَقَبَةٍ مُؤْمِنَةٍ.<a href="#p12" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p13"></span>-<span class="c5"> فَإِنْ عَجَزَ كَفِطْرَةٍ:</span> صَامَ ثَلَاثَةَ أَيَّامٍ مُتَتَابِعَةً.<a href="#p13" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p14"></span>-<span class="c5"> وَمَبْنَى يَمِينٍ:</span> عَلَى العُرْفِ.<a href="#p14" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p15"></span>- وَيُرْجَعُ فِيهَا إِلَى نِيَّةِ حَالِفٍ لَيْسَ ظَالِماً، إِنِ احْتَمَلَهَا لَفْظُهُ؛<span class="c5"> كَنِيَّتِهِ بِبِنَاءٍ وَسَقْفٍ:</span> السَّمَاءَ.<a href="#p15" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p> </div>